    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "pacific\nair\nlines\nflight\nschedule\nPACIFIC\neffective\njanuary 2,\n1968",
      "suddenly\nPacific Air\nis your hot line\nto fun country!\nPORTLAND\nCRESCENT\nCITY\nEUREKA\nARCATA\nRED BLUFF\n• CHICO\nMARYSVILLE —\nYUBA CITY\nSANTA POSA\nSAN FRANCISCO\nOAKLAND\nSAN JOSE\nMONTEREY\n— SALINAS\nSAN LUIS OBISPO\n— PASO ROBLES\nSANTA MARIA\nVANDENBERG A. F. B.\nSANTA BARBARA\nOXNARD — VENTURA\nORENO\nLAKE TAHOE\nSACRAMENTO\nSTOCKTON\nFRESNO\n• BAKERSFIELD\nLAS VEGAS\n• PALMDALE — LANCASTER\nHOLLYWOOD/ BURBANK\nLOS ANGELES\nLONG BEACH\nSAN DIEGO\nPACIFIC\nReno!\nFrom San Jose — Another jackpot winner —\ntake the Weekender — non-stop. New Boeing\n727 jets to fun country. Fridays and Sundays.\nFresno!\nFrom Los Angeles — fly the Hot Line — take\nthe fastest; the only pure jet service.\nFrom Sacramento — Brand new, fast, con-\nvenient jet-prop service, linking California's\nState Capitol with the San Joaquin Valley.\nFrom San Francisco — enjoy more time in\nfun country — fly the only pure jet service to\nFresno — the embarkation point for panoramic\nYosemite.\nhot line specialties…\nNew — fly the only direct jet props between\nStockton and Los Angeles.\nNew - Excursion fare between Hollywood /\nBurbank and Las Vegas. — $26.00 round-trip.\nNew — additional pure jet flights between Los\nAngeles and Monterey. Fridays and Sundays.\nNew — non-stop jet-prop service between\nBakersfield and San Francisco, daily."
    ],
